{"tid":2347834,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"蕭若元：若法院繼續給予保釋或令中共加快摧毁香港司法獨立！","createTime":"2020-12-31T10:21:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-31T10:23:49.000Z","uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"440ae95e27f1ef9e331ef2e9f06cb3c7cc1b2b88","tid":2347834,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T10:21:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/M7DKn0tygao\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FM7DKn0tygao&d=BLGvZshAgiFYydKSMDjJm%2Fno2Xhlbsa%2F7jwkLKy9%2F%2FE%3D&h=22b385fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/M7DKn0tygao</a><br />\n<br />\n蕭若元：<br />\n<br />\n若果法院繼續給予黎智英保釋，咁意味着香港嘅司法將會同北京硬碰，之後北京可能會加快摧毁香港司法系統。1998年終審法院都唔敢同中共硬碰，因為佢知道硬碰之下中共會打橫嚟，令到香港緊餘嘅司法獨立都會冇埋。<br />\n<br />\n法院考慮呢個問題需要有政治智慧。"},{"pid":"6985ca498151e6546d1886c24afae8862f6c6a41","tid":2347834,"uid":383914,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-31T10:23:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/lightbulb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />燈中左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}